  "title": "CCTV Service Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Conducting service and calibration procedures for spectrophotometers, color readers, illuminance meters, and light meters.</li><li>Performing calibration, repair, and maintenance tasks in accordance with standards set by the manufacturing facility in Japan.</li><li>Executing adjustments, alignments, replacements, and repairs of equipment and components as per equipment manuals and schematics, utilizing appropriate soldering tools.</li><li>Providing precise technical support by responding to customer inquiries via phone and email.</li><li>Ensuring accurate data entry and completion of service reports to comprehensively document all repair and calibration activities.</li><li>Monitoring repair cases to guarantee timely completion within the turnaround time specified by the factory guidelines.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Electrical & Electronics Engineering or relevant</li><li>Minimum with 2 year working experience in CCTV/ Security Industry</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
